      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Goal: The goal of the game is to guide the player through the solar system

    on
    their way to asteroid Psyche-16. However, the journey is not as empty as space
    may seem. The player will encounter unusual scenarios, and the solution they
    invent may provide them the boost the need to succeed.


    Set-Up: The user
    (you) selects an avatar to be on this journey. After this, determine which game
    mode you want to play. Select the number of CPU players whom you wish to be challenged
    against. At this time, also select any quality of life features you may want
    to use. When ready to begin your journey, press START.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
