      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Strategy: As the human player, you need to convince the judge that you
    deserve the best. This means you need to read into the other players' personalities
    to determine how they are going to play. Each Answer Card contains a list of
    4 personality traits. \n\nThrough observation, you may be able to determine which
    type of card personality a player will use, and then play a card of that type
    to influence them when they are the judge.\n\nDo the same when it is your turn
    as judge to ensure you don't accidently give another player a winning chance."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
